This project demonstrated how statistical analysis and probability concepts can be applied to startup funding data. The analysis identified several factors associated with funding success, including founder experience, revenue generation, growth rate, and industry sector. The findings can assist investors and startup accelerators in making more informed and data-driven investment decisions.

